
==Activating the extension==
Place one of these lines in your LocalSettings.php
(depending on the location you put your extensions in)

	require_once( "extensions/wiki-tools/StarterWiki/StarterWiki.php" );
	
		or 
	
	require_once( "extensions/StarterWiki/StarterWiki.php" );

==Activating the maintenance scripts==
Maintenance scripts must be placed within the "./maintenance" directory 
of your MediaWiki installation. In most cases, it is best to do this via 
a symbolic link, e.g.

% ln -s ./extensions/wiki-tools/StarterWiki/maintenance/createWikiDBFromStarter.php ./maintenance/

	or

% ln -s ./extensions/StarterWiki/maintenance/createWikiDBFromStarter.php ./maintenance/

Scripts can be run with a command line PHP call if your MediaWiki is 
properly configured to run maintenance scripts.
